If all the EnabledIfNot conditions you set for this menu item are false in QuickBooks, the menu item will be enabled. (That is, it will not be grayed out.)

Values:
AccountantCopyExists, AssemblyItemsEnabled, ClassesEnabled, EstimatesEnabled, HasCustomers, HasVendors, InventoryEnabled, IsAccountantCopy, MultiUserMode, PayrollEnabled, PriceLevelsEnabled, SalesOrdersEnabled, SalesTaxEnabled, TimeTrackingEnabled

No default value.
